#
# ~/.zlogin
# *finally* executed by a *login* zsh shell
# see man zsh(1)
#
# Credits:
# [1] Gentoo Wiki - X without Display Manager
#     https://wiki.gentoo.org/wiki/X_without_Display_Manager
